Marvin's Room;;1996;;PG-13;;Drama;;6.7;;Jerry Zaks;;Meryl Streep,Leonardo DiCaprio,Diane Keaton,Robert De Niro,Hume Cronyn,Gwen Verdon,Hal Scardino,Dan Hedaya,Margo Martindale,Cynthia Nixon,Kelly Ripa,John Callahan,Olga Merediz,Joe Lisi,Steve DuMouchel,Bitty Schram,Lizbeth Mackay,Helen Stenborg;;Years ago, the fiercely independent Lee took off for Ohio, while her older sister Bessie stayed home to look after their bedridden father, Marvin. Lee has troubles of her own, including her mischievous son Hank, who has a knack for burning down the neighborhood when she's not looking. Seventeen years since her last visit, and after an unexpected call from Bessie, Lee's packs up Hank and his younger brother Charlie for the trip home.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0116999/